<div class="page_header"><span class="page_header_span">Daughters of Khaine</span></div>
<div class="noprint">

</div>
<!--/noindex-->
<p class="legend ShowFluff">They crave battle and seek power through bloodshed, honouring their deity with every kill. Even their closest allies shudder to witness the gory rituals that renew and reinvigorate these graceful murderers. They are the Daughters of Khaine, and to cross blades with them is to invite death.</p>
This page contains all of the rules you need to field your Daughters of Khaine miniatures on the battlefields of the Mortal Realms, from a host of exciting allegiance abilities to a range of warscrolls and warscroll battalions. The rules are split into the following sections.<ul></ul>
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;"><div class="BreakInsideAvoid Corner3" style="padding:0px;max-width:988px;"><table class="frameDark collapse" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" ><tbody><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_1.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_2.png" style="height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_3.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td></tr><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_8.png" style="width:20px"></td><td bgcolor="#1d190d" style="color:#fefefe"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif; font-size:1em"><div class="contents_header">Contents</div><div class="NavColumns3"><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine#Books" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>ooks</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine#Designers-Commentary" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">D</b>esigners’ Commentary</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine#Battletome:-Daughters-of-Khaine" style="color:#fefefe">Battletome: Daughters of Khaine</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Allies" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">A</b>llies</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Battle-Traits" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>attle Traits</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Blood-Rites" style="color:#fefefe">Blood Rites</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Fanatical-Faith" style="color:#fefefe">Fanatical Faith</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Command-Traits" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">C</b>ommand Traits</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Artefacts-of-Power" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">A</b>rtefacts of Power</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Gifts-of-Morathi" style="color:#fefefe">Gifts of Morathi</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Artefacts-of-Shadow" style="color:#fefefe">Artefacts of Shadow</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Relics-of-Khaine" style="color:#fefefe">Relics of Khaine</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Spell-Lores" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">S</b>pell Lores</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Lore-of-Shadows" style="color:#fefefe">Lore of Shadows</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Prayers-of-the-Khainite-Cult" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">P</b>rayers of the Khainite Cult</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#The-Temples-of-Khaine" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">T</b>he Temples of Khaine</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Hagg-Nar" style="color:#fefefe">Hagg Nar</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Draichi-Ganeth" style="color:#fefefe">Draichi Ganeth</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#The-Kraith" style="color:#fefefe">The Kraith</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Khailebron" style="color:#fefefe">Khailebron</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><img class="tooltip logo2" title="Expansion. Broken Realms: Morathi (2th edition, version 1.0)" src="/aos/img/expansions/BR_logo2.png"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Zainthar-Kai" style="color:#fefefe">Zainthar Kai</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Battleplans" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>attleplans</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#The-Altar-of-War" style="color:#fefefe">The Altar of War</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Path-to-Glory" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">P</b>ath to Glory</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Daughters-of-Khaine-Warband-Tables" style="color:#fefefe">Daughters of Khaine Warband Tables</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Followers-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Followers Rewards Table</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/daughters-of-khaine/#Champion-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Champion Rewards Table</a></div></div></span></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_4.png" style="width:20px"></td></tr><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_7.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_6.png" style="height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_5.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
